Watchlist

Where to Watch

Cunning Hannibal Lecter resurfaces after a decade in hiding to toy with FBI agent Clarice Starling in this handsomely-mounted sequel. As Starling's career flounders, Lecter attempts to elude a greedy Italian police detective. Meanwhile, a maimed former victim of Lecter's plots revenge.
